resources.string:
"
1. To help you browse and edit CAD drawings, we will request storage permissions, camera and photo album permissions, and microphone permissions; if you want to display the shooting location in photos, we will request your location permission;
2. To provide you with account registration and upgrade services, we will request to collect account information and log information;
3. To help you and your friends carry out drawing-related projects and sharing, we will request clipboard reading permissions, address book access permissions, notification permissions, and permissions to connect to nearby devices;
4. For the purposes of information sharing, message pushing, third-party login, and comprehensive statistical analysis, we have integrated third-party SDKs, and the details of the permissions they request are listed in detail in the 《Privacy Policy》;
5. We will adopt various security technologies to protect your personal information, and we will not obtain, share, or provide your information to third parties without your consent;
6. You can access, correct, and delete your personal information, and we will also provide account cancellation and complaint channels."

"Jak wstawić blok o tej samej nazwie? 
1. W bibliotece bloków zmień nazwę bloku na tą samą nazwę;
2. Ponownie wykonaj operację wstawienia bloku."
